data.description: Beautiful  five bedroom, three bath all brick home just over two years old! Sitting on more than a quarter of an acre with huge above ground pool and plenty of backyard space for entertaining! Hardwoods throughout the entire main living space, granite countertops throughout kitchen and all three full baths. Gorgeous tiled walk in shower in master bath with dual vanities and two walk in closets. Giant fully finished, fully carpeted basement with 2 large bedrooms, two car garage with built in bar that owner is leaving! This home and its landscaping have been immaculately maintained.  NO City Taxes! 2 miles from Clarksville city limits! Excellent neighborhood, must see!
